## resets

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>` encoded as a list of phandle + reset-specifier pairs

A list of phandle and reset specifier pairs, one pair per reset signal consumed by the device. The number of cells in each reset specifier is determined by the `#reset-cells` property of the referenced reset controller node.

Used together with `reset-names` to identify each reset signal by name.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    resets = <&gcc GCC_QUPV3_WRAP1_S7_BCR>;
    reset-names = "qup";
};
```
